<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10875</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>象怪指着悟空。“他不是小妖，他是猴子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19550</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他不是一般的猴子。”大鹏怪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是孙悟空，抓住他！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狮怪扑了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空飞快地从洞里跑出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑到离洞很远的地方才停下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47696</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咻！”悟空自言自语道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51824</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好险啊。我好像笑得分了神，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以才变回了原形。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空回到唐僧他们那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么样了？”悟净问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那前面有很多妖怪吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>"我把所有的小妖都吓跑了。”悟空骄傲地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75819</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是，山里还有三个厉害的妖怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们打算抓住师父，再……吃了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！”唐僧喊道，差点晕倒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净扶住了他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您别担心，师父。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93899</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不会让妖怪们伤害您的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93900</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，我们得在过山之前，除掉妖怪们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>幸亏我们上山前知道了他们的计划。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧不安地握着双手点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空转身看着八戒和悟净。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要有人帮我一起除掉妖怪。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我和你一起去。”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在这里照顾师父。”悟净说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空和八戒朝洞口飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空拿出了金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130470</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒举起了钉耙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来和他们说。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要说什么？”八戒问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“说好话，让他们离开。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149275</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他转身看向洞口。“妖怪们！”他大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149282</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“马上离开这里！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150679</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>否则，我们就毁了山，除掉你们三个！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有一切都安静了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，狮怪从洞里出来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他比悟空和八戒都要大很多。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么在这里大喊？”狮怪冷冷地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你、象怪、还有大鹏怪，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马上离开这座山！”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们为什么要离开？”狮怪问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185618</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们没有欺负你啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185618</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你这妖怪！”悟空喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道你们要抓唐僧，而且还要吃了他！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们根本没碰唐僧。”狮怪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可是你，孙悟空！你把我们的小妖们都吓跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这里的你才是最坏的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不坏！”悟空喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿起金箍棒朝狮怪冲过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狮怪张大了嘴，露出锋利的尖牙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空挥舞金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狮怪扑过来。咕噜！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒吓得脸色苍白。“啊呃！”他大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236626</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那狮怪刚才吞掉了悟空！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239902</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒拼命地跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑到唐僧和悟净那里才停下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了？”悟净问，“悟空在哪儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“取经……现在……结束了。”八戒气喘吁吁地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空……被吃了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”唐僧大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273678</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒摇了摇头。“我们还是回家吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273678</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>与此同时，狮怪回到了洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抬头挺胸，微笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“外面出什么事了？”象怪问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把孙悟空吓跑了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还没有。”狮怪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那他在哪儿？”大鹏怪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狮怪拍了拍肚子。“在这里面。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你吃了他？”象怪问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“吃了。”狮怪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大鹏怪摇了摇头。“那可坏事儿了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么？”狮怪问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孙悟空是不会死的。”大鹏怪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他现在可能还在你肚子里活着。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对，我还活着。”悟空突然喊道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里面很好、很暖和！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>